-- Lombard Odier Hires Selectium Europe's Marc Bataillon for Hedge Fund Team
-- B y   W a r r e n   G i l e s
-- 2010-10-11T09:00:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/lombard-odier-hires-selectium-europe-s-marc-bataillon-for-hedge-fund-team.html
Lombard Odier Darier Hentsch & Cie.
said its Investment Managers business hired Marc Bataillon and
two others from Selectium Europe. Bataillon will report to Aziz
Nahas, chief executive officer at Lombard Odier Investment
Managers, the Geneva-based bank said today in an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Warren Giles at 
 wgiles@bloomberg.net  